        <Parent_String>Gulf Coast Mesoamerican styles [300108063], Mesoamerican regional styles and periods [300016992], Mesoamerican [300016959], Pre-Columbian Middle American styles and periods [300108028], Pre-Columbian (American) [300016619], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
